      "duration": 1.08,
      "size": 17280,
      "text": "欢迎来到傅里叶级数实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "傅里叶在研究热传导时发现了一个惊人的事实。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "任何周期函数，无论多么复杂，都可以表示为正弦和余弦函数的无穷级数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.41,
      "size": 22608,
      "text": "这个发现彻底改变了数学和物理学。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "傅里叶级数的形式是：常数项加上无穷多个正弦和余弦项的和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "每一项的频率是基频的整数倍，叫做谐波。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "傅里叶系数决定了每个谐波的振幅。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.31,
      "size": 21024,
      "text": "这些系数可以通过积分公式计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "square-wave",
      "line_id": "sq-1",
      "filename": "square-wave-sq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/square-wave-sq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.22,
      "size": 19440,
      "text": "让我们看看方波的傅里叶级数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "square-wave",
      "line_id": "sq-2",
      "filename": "square-wave-sq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/square-wave-sq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "方波只包含奇次谐波，系数按1/n递减。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "square-wave",
      "line_id": "sq-3",
      "filename": "square-wave-sq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/square-wave-sq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "随着项数增加，级数越来越接近方波。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "square-wave",
      "line_id": "sq-4",
      "filename": "square-wave-sq-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/square-wave-sq-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "但在跳变点附近，总有一些振荡，这就是吉布斯现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gibbs-1",
      "filename": "gibbs-gibbs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/gibbs-gibbs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "吉布斯现象是傅里叶级数在不连续点附近的过冲。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gibbs-2",
      "filename": "gibbs-gibbs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/gibbs-gibbs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "无论取多少项，过冲的幅度始终约为9%。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gibbs-3",
      "filename": "gibbs-gibbs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/gibbs-gibbs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "这不是计算误差，而是傅里叶级数的固有特性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gibbs-4",
      "filename": "gibbs-gibbs-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/gibbs-gibbs-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "在信号处理中，需要特别注意这个现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.31,
      "size": 21024,
      "text": "傅里叶级数是信号分析的基础。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "音乐合成器用它来创造各种音色。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "电路分析中，它用于研究周期信号的响应。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fourier-series",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fourier-series/xiaoxiao/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "图像压缩中的JPEG格式也基于类似的原理。"
    },
    {
